widgets_values: Here you can control the image size in megapixels while preserving the aspect ratio. The sides are scaled in steps of 16 pixels.
Here you can choose the sampler and scheduler. Denoising steps are controlled in a separate panel above, and CFG is fixed at 1.
Here you can independently control the number of highnoise and lownoise steps.

# Wan SVI 2 Pro FLF notes This workflow is built around Wan 2.2 + SVI 2.0 Pro and FLF (First/Last Frame) logic, with custom nodes for segment stitching and end control. ## Core idea - Use **SVI 2 Pro** for long, continuous motion across segments. - Use **FLF-style end control** to hard-lock the last frame (or block of frames) of each segment. - Use **WanCutLastSlot** to remove the last temporal slot before feeding latents into the next segment, to avoid over-constraining the very end. ## Note This should work with your current models that already handle standard SVI 2 PRO, but I can't test every single one. Start with your own model combo, and if the results aren't what you expect, use the finetuned model this setup was built around until a more universal solution appears. Here's the one I'm using, with speed LoRA baked in: - **High noise model**: [https://civitai.com/models/2053259?modelVersionId=2540892](https://civitai.com/models/2053259?modelVersionId=2540892) (NSFW warning) - **Low noise model**: [https://civitai.com/models/2053259?modelVersionId=2540896](https://civitai.com/models/2053259?modelVersionId=2540896) (NSFW warning) Any quantization should work fine. ## Useful links - SVI tutorial (video): [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-3DVJu72VhE](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-3DVJu72VhE) - Stable Video Infinity main page: [https://github.com/vita-epfl/Stable-Video-Infinity](https://github.com/vita-epfl/Stable-Video-Infinity) - KJNodes for ComfyUI: [https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-KJNodes](https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-KJNodes) - Wan 2.2 SVI 2 Pro native workflow (JSON example by KJ): [https://github.com/user-attachments/files/24359648/wan22_SVI_Pro_native_example_KJ.json](https://github.com/user-attachments/files/24359648/wan22_SVI_Pro_native_example_KJ.json) - Wan fp8 I2V models for ComfyUI: [https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy_fp8_scaled/tree/main/I2V](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy_fp8_scaled/tree/main/I2V) - Lightx2v Wan 2.2 Distill LoRAs: [https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Wan2.2-Distill-Loras/tree/main](https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Wan2.2-Distill-Loras/tree/main) - SVI 2.0 Pro LoRAs for Wan video: [https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/tree/main/LoRAs/Stable-Video-Infinity/v2.0](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/tree/main/LoRAs/Stable-Video-Infinity/v2.0) - Wan 2.2 I2V GGUF (for GGUF runtimes): [https://huggingface.co/QuantStack/Wan2.2-I2V-A14B-GGUF/tree/main](https://huggingface.co/QuantStack/Wan2.2-I2V-A14B-GGUF/tree/main)
